ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectComing into Force of the Canada-Argentine Republic Agreement on Social Security
PrecisOrder declaring that AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY BETWEEN CANADA AND THE ARGENTINE REPUBLIC enters into force on the first day of the fourth month after each Party receives from the other Party written notification through the diplomatic channel that it has complied with all internal requirements for the entry into force of this Agreement.
